                <![CDATA[<p>以前讲到电竞手提电脑，都是「大牛龟」又厚又重，而且风扇声超级嘈吵。不过在刚刚的 CES 2025 亮相的全新 ROG Flow Z13 (2025) ，薄到像一部平板电脑一样（事实上它可拆除键盘，变身平板电脑），可说是市场上少数兼具高效能与二合一灵活性的电竞装置。而这部手提电脑在外观设计上都展现独特风格，硬体规格也让人惊艳，今次小编就借到这部新机，同大家睇睇这部真正可以轻便带出街玩的电竞手提电脑。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294109" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05045-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05045-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05045.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294110" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05068-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05068-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05068.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>外观设计与机身结构</h2><p>ROG Flow Z13 (2025) 采用坚固的金属材质机身，部分 CNC 切割工艺确保装置的耐用度。背面搭载 RGB 灯效视窗，光线透过金属切割缝隙散发，营造极具科技感的氛围，别具有 ROG 产品风格。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294124" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05045-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05045-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05045-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294122" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05038-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05038-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05038.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294123" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05036-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05036-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05036.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>这部手提电脑作为电竞机，重量只约 1.2 kg，虽然相较于其他 2 合 1 平板稍微厚重，但考虑到高阶硬体配置还有散热系统，这样的重量仍在可接受范围内。机身背部配备 1300 万像素后置镜头与 500 万像素前置镜头，方便视讯会议或文件扫描。</p><h2>操作方式与使用体验</h2><p>ROG Flow Z13 延续 2 合 1 设计，搭载可拆卸键盘，使用者可自由切换手提电脑与平板模式。这个键盘是另一个小编十分喜欢的地方，它虽未采用机械轴设计，但键程适中且回馈感良好，触控板则具备玻璃材质与震动回馈机制，操控手感优异，考虑到它是可拆除设计，质感同触感都令人满足。键盘 RGB 灯效可作为附加的衬托。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294116" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05069-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05069-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05069.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294117" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05049-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05049-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05049.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲背面以及键盘的 RGB 灯效</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294118" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05055-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05055-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05055.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可以拆卸的键盘</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294119" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05056-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05056-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05056.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲拆除后电脑便变成平板电脑，支援触控操作</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294120" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05060-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05060-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05060.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用手指或触控笔都可操作电脑</p><p>ROG Flow Z13 随附 ASUS Pen 触控笔，提供更直觉的输入方式，适合绘图、笔记或签名用途。虽然键盘仅能透过物理连接使用，未提供蓝牙无线模式，但小编反而喜欢这种较实在的连接方法，重点是只要轻易磁吸上去就可用到，整体使用体验流畅。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294134" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05047-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05047-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05047.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294135" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05054-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05054-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05054.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲作为一部二合一电脑，它的键盘当然可摊开到 180 度也可拆除</p><p>这部电脑的萤幕为 13 吋 Quad HD IPS 面板，更新率高达 180Hz，反应时间为 3ms，确保游戏画面流畅稳定。亮度方面最高达 500 尼特，虽不及 OLED，但考量到成本与续航力，此选择仍属合理。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294121" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05043-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05043-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05043.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>
